The Chronicle Chronicle Online Reporter Abundant Life Revival Mission international founder and lead pastor, prophet Itayi Ukama last week Tuesday celebrated his birthday at Cresta Churchill Hotel in Bulawayo. <img class="wp-image-611503 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-3.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-3.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-3-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The Ukama family He turned 52. <img class="wp-image-611502 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-4.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-4.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-4-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The Ukamas with pastor Joseph Masaiti and Mrs Cherish Masaiti Prophet Ukama’s birthday celebrations, held on Tuesday night, were graced by church members and family. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611493 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-9.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-9.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-9-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Over the years the church he leads has embarked on philanthropic works that have seen it send under privileged children to school. <img class="wp-image-611475 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-17.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-17.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-17-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The cake The church has also hosted health expos in rural areas in Matabeleland North and South. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611497 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-7.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-7.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-7-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The last expo was held in Lupane’s Ndwane area where over a thousand villagers benefited from a free medical outreach programme organised by Abundant Life Revival Mission International Church in partnership with health service providers from Bulawayo. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611472 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-18.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-18.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-18-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The one-day medical outreach was held at Ndwane Primary School on Saturday. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611505 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-2.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-2.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-2-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> 12 doctors, who included dentists, opticians, ophthalmologists, general practitioners and other health providers made up the team that donated their time and expertise to attend to people with various ailments. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611470 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-19.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-19.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-19-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The goals of Abundant Life Revival Mission International Church are to: “affect and to influence Communities for Christ, not only through preaching the gospel but by also undertaking projects to facilitate infrastructural development of those communities. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611481 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-13.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-13.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-13-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> “To minister emotional, spiritual and physical healing to all who would run to the Lord for salvation. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611496 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-8.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-8.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-8-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> “To build up strong families that will influence communities, cities and nations. <img class="wp-image-611506 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-1.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-1.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-1-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Prophet Itayi Ukama “To raise and develop strong, influential and vibrant leaders who shall impact the whole world in various disciplines and spheres of life. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611479 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-14.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-14.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-14-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> “To propagate the gospel of Jesus Christ and spread its influence through deployment of missions to various parts of the world as well as planting churches. <img class="alignnone wp-image-611484 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-12.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-12.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/05/Ukama-birthday-celebrations-12-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> “To propagate Jesus Christ as the Good Samaritan to the needy, heartbroken, sick, wounded and disfranchised members of the society through charitable work.” <img class="alignnone wp-image-611499 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uplo